items.title: io.nashid.verify:sdk 2.6.1 发布, UI Improvements to Camera and Instruction Overlay Adjusted the camera background opacity to reduce background distractions during both liveness and ID scanning. Repositioned instruction text overlays and enhanced clarity. NFC Cancel Behaviour Added support for the new feature flag called “Count NFC Cancel.” When enabled, pressing the Cancel button during NFC reading will count as an attempt toward the retry limit. When disabled, canceling will not be counted — allowing users to retry NFC scanning without reducing their available attempts.

items.title: net.linlan.emis:emis-java-backend 1.0.0 发布, 基于JAVA开发的企业级多身份管理系统后端工程，基于Springboot，采用支持 JAVA 1.8最高版本的framework、security，后端数据访问采用Mybatis框架，支持多种数据库一套代码适配，提供脚手架可快速生成Mapper等，在仓库功能上，借鉴主流的SSO和IAM框架，实现统一用户管理。前端提供VUE框架和REACT框架的控制台管理工程、企业个人门户工程和移动端应用扩展。
